528
00:38:49,068 --> 00:38:50,802
It had nothing to
do with drugs.

529
00:38:50,837 --> 00:38:52,903
L.T., this is a waste
of our damn time.

530
00:38:52,937 --> 00:38:54,680
I think sergeant
Doakes is right.

531
00:38:54,708 --> 00:38:56,933
I read the other reports,
all the other forensic analysis.

532
00:38:56,968 --> 00:39:00,170
Everyone agrees the cokehead murders
had nothing to do with cocaine.

533
00:39:00,205 --> 00:39:01,933
It was a crime of passion.

534
00:39:01,968 --> 00:39:04,650
The murderer came to kill
the woman, not the dealer.

535
00:39:04,676 --> 00:39:06,002
He did him quick and
got him out of the way.

536
00:39:06,037 --> 00:39:08,573
But he sure as hell took his
sweet time slicing up that lady,

537
00:39:08,608 --> 00:39:11,001
and you don't do that
unless you have a close,

