549
00:41:11,408 --> 00:41:15,012
No. Oh, god.

550
00:41:15,038 --> 00:41:17,853
Talk to me about Jane Saunders.

551
00:41:18,465 --> 00:41:20,932
Okay.
I did her.

552
00:41:20,968 --> 00:41:24,610
- How?
