00:45:00,565 --> 00:45:02,801
Give us a minute.

569
00:45:03,335 --> 00:45:05,863
Hanging in there?

570
00:45:06,068 --> 00:45:08,710
This will teach me to tailgate.

571
00:45:08,857 --> 00:45:10,701
Let's go over this again.

572
00:45:10,737 --> 00:45:14,603
- I'm all yours.
